      },
      "lineNbr": 573,
      "author": {
        "id": 1001939
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-06T09:35:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The system has two devices named \"Fan Board 1\" because of the mechanical design. The fan boards for the upper eight blades and the lower eight blades are installed in opposite orientations. Therefore, the \"Upper\" and \"Lower\" parameters are used to differentiate them.",
